narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Action Urgent Care INC is a Clinic/Center  Urgent Care provider based in San Jose, CA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $44.7M in Medicaid payments across 622K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $44.7M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
